OL,3,CStone Roses bassist Mani to be
OL,4,Chonoured with mural
OL,6,FA fundraiser has been set up for a
OL,7,Fpermanent mural to the late Stone
OL,8,FRoses and Primal Scream bassist, Mani
OL,9,F- and all of the profits will be
OL,10,Fdonated to the cancer centre where his
OL,11,Fwife was treated.
OL,13,FMani, whose full name was Gary
OL,14,FMounfield, died of "respiratory
OL,15,Fissues" linked to a long-standing lung
OL,16,Fcondition in November 2025 at the age
OL,17,Fof 63.
