OL,3,CStone Roses bassist Mani to be
OL,4,Chonoured with mural
OL,6,FThe bassist was part of the original
OL,7,FStone Roses' line-up alongside singer
OL,8,FBrown, guitarist John Squire and
OL,9,Fdrummer Alan 'Reni' Wren.
OL,11,FNow, a campaign has been launched on
OL,12,FCrowdfunder which aims to install a
OL,13,Flarge mural painting of the music
OL,14,Flegend in in Failsworth, where he grew
OL,15,Fup.
OL,17,FGRIT Studios, the not-for-profit art
OL,18,Fstudios organisation, has stepped
OL,19,Fforward to organise a community-led,
OL,20,Fcrowdfunded project that celebrates
OL,21,FMani's life, music and spirit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
