OL,3,CStone Roses bassist Mani to be
OL,4,Chonoured with mural
OL,6,FOrganisers say donations will fund the
OL,7,Fmural and all profits will go to
OL,8,FMaggie's Manchester, which was close
OL,9,Fto Mani and his wife Imelda's hearts
OL,10,Fduring her cancer treatment.
OL,12,FThe idea for a permanent tribute came
OL,13,Fafter bandmate and Roses frontman Ian
OL,14,FBrown delivered a eulogy during his
OL,15,Ffuneral service at Manchester
OL,16,FCathedral in December.
OL,18,FIan stated he would love to see a "50-
OL,19,Ffoot gold statue" of Mani erected to
OL,20,Fcommemorate his life and career.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
