OL,3,CStone Roses bassist Mani to be
OL,4,Chonoured with mural
OL,6,FIf the goal is reached, the artwork
OL,7,Fwill be created by Pic.One.Art who
OL,8,Falso created the Liam and Noel
OL,9,FGallagher mural in Burnage ahead of
OL,10,FOasis' comeback shows.
OL,12,FMani's brother, Greg Mounfield, is
OL,13,Fsupporting this campaign and has
OL,14,Ffacilitated a prominent large wall
OL,15,Fspace for the mural and chosen the
OL,16,Fdesign.
OL,18,FMounfield was part of The Stone Roses'
OL,19,Fclassic line-up alongside singer
OL,20,FBrown, guitarist John Squire and
OL,21,Fdrummer Alan 'Reni' Wren.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
