OL,3,CStone Roses bassist Mani to be
OL,4,Chonoured with mural
OL,6,FHe worked on the band's 1989 debut
OL,7,Falbum, which featured hits such as I
OL,8,FWanna Be Adored and She Bangs The
OL,9,FDrums, which is underpinned by his
OL,10,Fprowling bassline, and its harder-
OL,11,Frocking 1994 follow-up Second Coming.
OL,13,FAfter the Manchester band broke-up in
OL,14,F1996, Mounfield joined Primal Scream,
OL,15,Fworking on several albums together.
OL,16,FBut he decided to left the band in
OL,17,F2011 to reform The Stone Roses.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
