OL,3,CStone Roses bassist Mani to be
OL,4,Chonoured with mural
OL,6,FThe bass player was due to embark on a
OL,7,Fspeaking tour in September 2026,
OL,8,Fcalled The Stone Roses, Primal Scream,
OL,9,FAnd Me, which was due to see him
OL,10,Freflect on his life in rock and roll.
OL,12,FMounfield married his late wife Imelda
OL,13,Fafter the two met during the 13-month
OL,14,Frecording of Second Coming at
OL,15,FRockfield Studios in Monmouth, Wales,
OL,16,Fand they had two sons together.
OL,18,FAway from music, the Manchester-born
OL,19,Fstar was a keen fan of Manchester
OL,20,FUnited, and often spoke about the team
OL,21,Fon TV and radio.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
